DESCRIPTION:Brief Description: \nNever swam before? No problem! These less
 ons will give you the important foundational skills in swimming and help 
 you be more comfortable in the pool. Learn how to use proper breath contr
 ol\, float\, and swim with a kickboard. \nSkills Focus:\n\nBeing comforta
 ble in the water\nLearning how to float on your back and front\nLearning 
 how to kick off the wall with a kickboard\nIntroducing proper breath cont
 rol in the water\nLearning how to tread water\nLearn alternate kicks (Fro
 ggy Kick)\nBeing comfortable in the deep end \nIntroducing arms to your s
 trokes\n\nHow do I Sign-up?\n\nRegistration is not required\nFREE with a 
 valid Montclair State ID\n\nWhen and Where?\n\nMonday: 1-2PM & 5-6PM\nStu
 dent Recreation Center - Pool \n\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAddit
 ional Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engag
 e/event/11931610
DTEND:20260323T180000Z
DTSTAMP:20260323T025109Z
DTSTART:20260323T170000Z
LOCATION:Student Recreation Center - Pool
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Free Swim Lessons *Beginner*
UID:https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11931610
URL:https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11931610
X-HOSTS:Campus Recreation
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Montclair State University
CATEGORIES:Athletics
DESCRIPTION:Take your swimming to the next level! Get introduced to new st
 rokes or work on the ones you already know. These lessons are for swimmer
 s who are a little more comfortable in the water but still want to improv
 e their technique and expand what skills they know. \n \nSkills Focus:\n\
 nSwimming unassisted on your front and back \nImprove treading (in the de
 ep end)\nImproving breath control in the water\nLearn alternate kicks (Do
 lphin Kick)\nIntroduction to and/or improving your breaststroke\nSwimming
  laps\nIntroduction to open and flip turns\nIntroduction to Butterfly\n\n
 How do I Sign-up?\n\nRegistration is not required\nFREE with a valid Mont
 clair State ID\n\nWhen and Where?\n\nMonday: 1-2PM & 5-6PM\nStudent Recre
 ation Center - Pool \n\n\nHosted by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional Info
 rmation can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/11
 933922
