BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Montclair State University
CATEGORIES:Athletics
DESCRIPTION:Take your swimming to the next level! Get introduced to new st
 rokes or work on the ones you already know. These lessons are for swimmer
 s who are a little more comfortable in the water but still want to improv
 e their technique and expand what skills they know. \n \nSkills Focus:\n\
 nSwimming unassisted on your front and back \nImprove treading (in the de
 ep end)\nImproving breath control in the water\nLearn alternate kicks (Do
 lphin Kick)\nIntroduction to and/or improving your breaststroke\nSwimming
  laps\nIntroduction to open and flip turns\nIntroduction to Butterfly\n\n
