BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Montclair State University
CATEGORIES:ThoughtfulLearning
CATEGORIES:Academic/Educational
CATEGORIES:Orientation
DESCRIPTION:Hi\,\nCLaSE - Center for Latino heritage and Spanish language 
 Excellence - is launching a new program after listening to our students f
 eedback and needs:\nUndergraduate Certificate in Applied Spanish for the 
 Professions\nLaunching in Fall 2026\, this innovative program is designed
  for students who want to strengthen their Spanish language skills while 
 preparing for careers that serve diverse communities.\nStudents can choos
 e from three professional tracks tailored to their career interests:\n\n\
 nSpanish for Health Professionals\n\n\nSpanish for Justice Studies\n\n\nS
 panish for Business\n\n\nThrough practical coursework and real-world comm
 unication skills\, students will learn how to use Spanish effectively in 
 professional settings such as healthcare\, legal and community services\,
  and business environments. Use your elective courses\, take 12 credits w
 hile completing the credits for your major and graduate with a title that
  certifies you to serve the Spanish speaking communities in your field.\n
 In today’s multilingual society\, the ability to communicate across langu
 ages and cultures is a powerful professional asset. This certificate help
 s students build career-ready language skills\, cultural competence\, and
  confidence while making a meaningful impact in Spanish-speaking communit
 ies.\nDuring this info session\, we will explain details and answer to al
 l questions.\n\nHosted by: Center for Latino Heritage & Spanish Language 
 Excellence\, Spanish and Latino Studies\n\nOnline Location: https://montc
 lair.zoom.us/my/antonella.calarota?omn=95211227398\n\nAdditional Informat
 ion can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/123340
 26
DTEND:20260324T190000Z
DTSTAMP:20260323T025109Z
DTSTART:20260324T180000Z
LOCATION:Online
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Info Session for the new UG Certificate in Applied Spanish for the
  Professions - 3 tracks: Health professionals\, Business\, Justice Studie
 s
