BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Montclair State University
CATEGORIES:Athletics
DESCRIPTION:\n\nTake your swimming to the next level! Get introduced to ne
 w strokes or work on the ones you already know. These lessons are for swi
 mmers who are a little more comfortable in the water but still want to im
 prove their technique and expand what skills they know. \n \nSkills Focus
