DESCRIPTION:Join the brothers of Sigma Lambda Beta International Fraternit
 y\, Incorporated for our “Pie a Beta” fundraiser! Stop by and take part i
 n the fun by getting the chance to pie a brother\, whipped cream\, laughs
 \, and good vibes guaranteed. It’s a lighthearted way to support our chap
